{"tid":1364994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7.27反黑為人民 We Connect！】  護送市民服務，及司機大佬義載市民撤退","createTime":"2019-07-25T13:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:57:36.000Z","uid":54684,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d4160e67e5305f047f4b597afa5a5a2e150ae89a","tid":1364994,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"如果當日到時有咩不安全既情況，令一眾和理非市民安全受威脅<br />\n不妨考慮以下<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">WE CONNECT</span></strong>策略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>1) 人民衛隊︰</strong>建議義士以保護市民為第一要旨，護送人民安全撤退，係no. 1既考慮，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好依賴警方安排喇，自己的人民自己保護，保護人民靠義士，義士係人民既朋友，we connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>順便做到文宣效果<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2) 義載人民服務︰</strong>如果有手足有車，又肯捱義氣，萬一當日又好似721恐怖襲擊咁，列車都唔停站，警察又唔support，市民走唔到，隨時直接以車反覆地義載市民離開，去附近安全地方放低<br />\n<br />\n對付&quot;國人眾&quot;反而次要，對付極都有，呢個反而放次要D，我朋友已經另文講左<br />\n今次和理非反而係main pt<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356912</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">利申︰以上皆假設最後7.27反黑遊行係合法，絕不建議任何違法行為</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659af0d1ee49c543c92f1d71b5a4f26f69570863","tid":1364994,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f531b9461082cd8713ea808db5e7931ca6177bc","tid":1364994,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:36:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8bd1ebb347d35a44b23b66f5e9308b342126a4","tid":1364994,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ac667eef59c6a74f656ef8